    "description_long": "This grave yard object consists of a rectangular tiled base supporting two black headstones, a wooden cross, and a rectangular plaque. The headstones are polished black stone, one featuring an engraved portrait and Cyrillic inscriptions, while the other has a carved epitaph and a decorative motif. The wooden cross stands between the headstones, contrasting with the dark stone. Two rectangular grave frames are set into the tiled base, marking burial plots. The plaque at the side is likely for additional inscriptions or dedications. The overall design is somber and formal, with a focus on symmetry and memorialization.",
